---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Corney's Automotive Services" description="Privacy Policy for Corney's Automotive Services, Taree NSW.">
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Corney's Automotive Services (ABN 72 659 468 550) operates a motor vehicle repair workshop at 16 Albert Lane, Taree NSW 2430. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you interact with us — including through our website and booking forms.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">2. What information we collect</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">We collect personal information that you provide to us directly, including:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>Your name</li>
            <li>Phone number and/or email address</li>
            <li>Vehicle details (make, model, year, registration number)</li>
            <li>Service history and job descriptions relating to your vehicle</li>
            <li>Any additional information you provide when booking or making an enquiry</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">We do not collect payment card details through our website. Payments are processed in-person at our workshop.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. How we use your information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">We use your information to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>Process and confirm your booking or service enquiry</li>
            <li>Contact you about your booking, vehicle, or quote</li>
            <li>Maintain a service history for your vehicle</li>
            <li>Send you service reminders (if you have opted in)</li>
            <li>Comply with our legal obligations</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">We do not use your information for marketing purposes without your explicit consent, and we do not sell your information to third parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4. How we store your information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Your information is stored securely in our workshop management system (MechanicDesk), which is hosted by Autodeck Pty Ltd. We take reasonable steps to protect your information from misuse, loss, and unauthorised access. Our systems are password-protected and access is limited to workshop staff.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">5. Who we share your information with</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">We may share your information with:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Parts suppliers</strong> — only to the extent necessary to order parts for your vehicle (vehicle details only, no personal contact information)</li>
            <li><strong>NSW Roads &amp; Maritime Services / Transport for NSW</strong> — as required for safety inspections (Pink Slips and Blue Slips)</li>
            <li><strong>Our service providers</strong> — who assist with operating our business (e.g. our workshop management software), under confidentiality obligations</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">We do not share your information with any other third parties without your consent.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">6. Your rights</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Under the Australian Privacy Act 1988, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request that we correct inaccurate information</li>
            <li>Request that we delete your information (subject to any legal obligations we have to retain it)</li>
            <li>Opt out of service reminders at any time</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">To make any of these requests, contact us at <a href="tel:0265526131" class="text-red-600 hover:underline">(02) 6552 6131</a> or visit us at 16 Albert Lane, Taree NSW 2430.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">7. Cookies and website analytics</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Our website may use standard analytics tools (such as Google Analytics) to understand how visitors use the site. This data is anonymised and does not identify individual visitors. You can opt out of analytics tracking through your browser settings.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">8. Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The current version will always be available on this page with the date it was last updated.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">9. Contact us</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your information, please contact us:</p>
          <div class="mt-3 text-gray-600">
            <p><strong>Corney's Automotive Services</strong></p>
            <p>16 Albert Lane, Taree NSW 2430</p>
            <p>Phone: <a href="tel:0265526131" class="text-red-600 hover:underline">(02) 6552 6131</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
